# DQN (Deep Q-Learning)

Implements a Deep Q-Learning (DQL) agent for quadrotor control and fault tolerance. Includes:

- `dql_agent.py`: DQL agent implementation (PyTorch)
- `dql_quad_env.py`: Custom quadrotor environment for DQL
- `maindql.py`: Training loop for DQL agent
- `watch_simulation.py`: Visualize trained agent in simulation
- `dql_quad_weights.pth`: Pretrained weights

## Usage
Run `maindql.py` to train the agent, or `watch_simulation.py` to view a trained agent.

Dependencies: torch, numpy, matplotlib, pybullet
